title: Can Turnbull court the progressive vote and maintain the hardline asylum seeker policy?
text: Malcolm Turnbull is riding a wave of positive poll results as he wins over progressive voters. But the issue of asylum seekers, and particularly that of the women allegedly raped on Nauru, will put this to the test. ...
